videos.description: SE Louisiana and Incarnate Word go back-and-forth in the final 11 seconds to somehow get to overtime.

videos.headline: Crazy sequence sends Southland tournament final to OT

videos.description: Jaaucklyn Moore gets the roll on the jumper for a two-point lead. Incarnate Word then gets a late stop sending them to the tournament for the first time in school history.
